[49m[38;5;9m- 103     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m **Amazon SNS for alert routing.** When trajectory analysis produces an alert, it needs to reach the right person through the right channel. SNS handles fan-out to multiple subscribers: pager, EHR notification, nursing station dashboard, charge nurse summary. Topic-based routing allows different alert severities to reach different endpoints.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      103[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Amazon SNS for alert routing.** When trajectory analysis produces an alert, it needs to reach the right person through the right channel. SNS handles fan-out to multiple subscribers: pager, EHR notification, nursing station dashboard, charge nurse summary. Topic-based routing allows different alert severities to reach different endpoints. All subscription endpoints (pager API, dashboard webhook, EHR integration) must be covered under your organization's BAA chain. An alert containing vital signs and patient identifiers is PHI regardless of the delivery channel.
